The pattern is always:

for(each node/cell) {

    if(not visited) {

        count++;

        dfs(...);
    }
}

Code

int countComponents(int n,
                    List<List<Integer>> graph)
{
    boolean[] visited = new boolean[n];

    int count = 0;

    for(int node = 0; node < n; node++) {

        if(!visited[node]) {

            count++;

            dfs(node, graph, visited);
        }
    }

    return count;
}

